I was angry and crying."
She took a return flight and flew home the next day.
After landing at 11pm, she took her six-year-old daughter from her father's house and decided they would both go to Ferguson the next morning.
What happened to Ferrell and Ferguson over the next nearly three years was the subject of a new documentary, "Whose Streets?," which will be released on August 11.
